    <item>
      <title>英国议会投票后被拒之门外 预示英国陷入资金危机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/uk-local-governments-locked-out-of-funding-points-to-crisis-after-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国一些资金最为匮乏的市政厅被排除在重要的短期资金来源之外，这预示着英国政府在 7 月 4 日大选后将面临严重的财政困境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/uk-local-governments-locked-out-of-funding-points-to-crisis-after-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 10:01:29 GMT</pubDate>
